The leaderboard command shows the top 50 players on the achievement
ladder.

Syntax:

  leaderboard

This leaderboard is based on total achievement tiers unlocked. It also
shows completed achievement lines and each player's equipped achievement
title.

If you want the endless dungeon rankings instead, use:

  eternal leaderboard

If you want your personal achievement journal, use:

  achievements

See also: help achievements, help eternal_dungeon
